							<h2 class="blog-title"><a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/cognitive-feedback/" title="Permalink to Cognitive Feedback">Cognitive Feedback</a></h2>							<div class="entry-meta"><span class="date"><a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/cognitive-feedback/" title="Cognitive Feedback"><time datetime="2018-02-12T23:03:06+00:00"><span class="date-month">12 de Fevereiro de 2018</span></time></a></span><span class="author"><a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/author/reginaldosantos-br/" title="View all posts by reginaldosantos.br" rel="author">reginaldosantos.br</a></span><span class="category"><a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/category/hackathons/" rel="category tag">Hackathons</a>, <a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/category/projects/" rel="category tag">Projects</a></span><span class="tags"><a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/tag/angular-js/" rel="tag">Angular.js</a>, <a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/tag/ibm-cloud/" rel="tag">IBM Cloud</a>, <a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/tag/node-red/" rel="tag">Node-red</a>, <a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/tag/node-js/" rel="tag">Node.js</a>, <a href="http://localhost:8080/index.php/tag/watson/" rel="tag">Watson</a></span></div>							<p>Cognitive Feedback App is the Agile approach to giving and receiving feedback. Give / Request feedback Contribute to the development of your team and colleagues by providing instant feedback. Using Natural Language makes the feedback more efficient. The app extracts the tone from the feedback and rank it accordingly.</p>

